** system elements
  -- components
     operating parts of the system described by input, process, and output
     -> elements of the system perform functions that perform the processes

  -- attributes
     properties of the components, or of the system under consideration

  -- relationships
     links between components and attributes


** system component types
  - structural components
     static, but still perform an operation (or function)
  - operating components
  -- perform processing or control (do or change something)
  -- flow components ...


** system definition
   - systems and subsystems
   -- systems, segments, subsystems, elements
      -> it look fractal - similar look at different magnifications

  -- environment

